Create .env.local manually in your project root with these contents:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
  # ===========================================                                                                                                                                                               # Converso Environment Variables
  # ===========================================

  # DATABASE (Required)
  # PostgreSQL connection string (Neon/Supabase)
  POSTGRES_URL="postgresql://username:password@host:5432/database?sslmode=require"

  # AUTHENTICATION (Required)
  # Generate with: openssl rand -base64 32
  AUTH_SECRET="generate-a-random-secret-here"
  NEXTAUTH_URL="http://localhost:3000"

  # OPENAI (Required)
  OPENAI_API_KEY="sk-..."

  # STRIPE (Required for billing)
  # Get from: https://dashboard.stripe.com/apikeys
  STRIPE_SECRET_KEY="sk_test_..."
  STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY="pk_test_..."
  STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET="whsec_..."

  # APPLICATION (Required)
  NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL="http://localhost:3000"
  ADMIN_EMAIL="your-email@example.com"

To get your keys:
  ┌────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
  │        Variable        │                             Where to get it                              │
  ├────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
  │ POSTGRES_URL           │ Neon dashboard → Connection string, or Supabase → Settings → Database    │
  ├────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
  │ AUTH_SECRET            │ Run: openssl rand -base64 32 in terminal                                 │
  ├────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
  │ OPENAI_API_KEY         │ https://platform.openai.com/api-keys                                     │
  ├────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
  │ STRIPE_SECRET_KEY      │ https://dashboard.stripe.com/apikeys (use sk_test_ for dev)              │
  ├────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
  │ STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY │ Same Stripe page (pk_test_)                                              │
  ├────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
  │ STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET  │ Stripe CLI: stripe listen --forward-to localhost:3000/api/stripe/webhook │
  └────────────────────────┴─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────